Package: FoSIntro
Title: Convenience functions for semiparametric function-on-scalar regressions
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Alexander", "Bauer", email = "alexander.bauer@stat.uni-muenchen.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package includes the appendix code for Bauer et al. (2018) 'An introduction to semiparametric function-on-scalar regression' and comprises several convenient functions for the workflow with function-on-scalar regression models estimated with 'refund::pffr'.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: parallel,
    refund,
    ggplot2,
    grid,
    gridExtra,
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    RColorBrewer,
    mgcv,
    tidyr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
